===Splitbark scrolls===
''There is a 1/51 (1/49 if wearing a [[ring of wealth]]) chance of rolling the splitbark scrolls drop table, if the previous tables are not reached. The tree wizards' journal and bloody notes will be given out only if the player has not received the books.''
